data.description: Welcome to charming living in the heart of Zanesville's north end! This adorable three-bedroom, one-bath home is nestled in a prime location close to shopping and stores, offering convenience at your doorstep. Kitchen includes granite countertops and the warmth of wood floors throughout, creates  a welcoming atmosphere for family and guests alike. Basement offers additional  space for hobbies or storage.  Outside, a special backyard awaits, providing the perfect space for outdoor gatherings or simply enjoying the tranquility of your own private space. Don't miss the chance to call this delightful abode your own!
